    {
      "id": "6a43dfa46eb40600000030e0d0",
      "text": "第27週: 日月火[[水]]木金土",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782833060,
      "updated": 1782833060
    },
    {
      "id": "6a43dfa46eb406000000dbbb0c",
      "text": "2026年 49.86％経過",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782833060,
      "updated": 1782833060
    },
    {
      "id": "6a44175300000000005fed9a",
      "text": " 50%ではないんだ[wogikaze.icon]",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1782847315,
      "updated": 1782847318
    },
    {
      "id": "6a43dfa46eb406000000bdfc4c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782833060,
      "updated": 1782833060
    },
    {
      "id": "6a43e4a10000000000454803",
      "text": "[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782834338,
      "updated": 1782834338
    },
    {
      "id": "6a43e4a20000000000454804",
      "text": "\t[https://inajob-with-ai.pages.dev/#/README inajob with AI 構造化ノート]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782834338,
      "updated": 1782834366
    },
    {
      "id": "6a43e4be0000000000454807",
      "text": "\t\t[grasp]に自分の日記と井戸端を食わせながら、構造化ノートを作ってもらっている",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782834366,
      "updated": 1782834390
    },
    {
      "id": "6a43e53a0000000000454808",
      "text": "\t\tAIの出力を自分の日記に混ぜるのは微妙と思ったので、日記を生データとしてAIと[inajob.icon]で改めて構造を写し取るような仕組みにしてみた",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782834491,
      "updated": 1782834539
    },
    {
      "id": "6a43eaa70000000000454809",
      "text": "\t\t構造化しないと重複まみれでどうしようもなくなるな・・",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782835880,
      "updated": 1782835889
    },
    {
      "id": "6a441ca6000000000072119a",
      "text": "\t\t>「結局日記に書いた内容から、その日記以上に面白いものを作り出すことは原理的に難しい」という根本的な限界",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1782848679,
      "updated": 1782848682
    },
    {
      "id": "6a441ca9000000000072119b",
      "text": "\t\t\tなるほど[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1782848682,
      "updated": 1782848686
    },
    {
      "id": "6a43dfa46eb406000000c067dd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782833060,
      "updated": 1782833060
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4417090000000000fc52a2",
      "text": "[wogikaze.icon]",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1782847242,
      "updated": 1782847242
    },
    {
      "id": "6a44170d0000000000fc52a5",
      "text": " [関連ページリストのソート順]が1タップで切り替えられるようになってる",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1782847246,
      "updated": 1782847335
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4417090000000000fc52a3",
      "text": "  [https://gyazo.com/913158bf9a1a9315e1896512bc90fbd1]",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1782847242,
      "updated": 1782847326
    },
    {
      "id": "6a44176d00000000005fed9b",
      "text": "  そんなに切り替える機会はないけど",
      "userId": "64099110a39a5c001c8a016e",
      "created": 1782847342,
      "updated": 1782847347
